== Minor edits ==

Is there any specific reason that this checkbox is disabled for IP editors? No opinion on whether it should be or not, I'm just curious because I'm so used to seeing it there. [[Special:Contributions/206.117.89.4|206.117.89.4]] ([[User talk:206.117.89.4|talk]]) 09:53, 24 April 2014 (UTC) ([[User:Ansh666]])

:[[Help:Minor edit]] says: "Users who are not [[Help:Logging in|logged in]] to {{SITENAME}} are not permitted to mark changes as minor because of the potential for vandalism. The ability to mark changes as minor is [[Wikipedia:Why create an account?#More editing features|one of many reasons to register]]." It has been there since the page creation in 2004. [[User:PrimeHunter|PrimeHunter]] ([[User talk:PrimeHunter|talk]]) 10:53, 24 April 2014 (UTC)

::Ah, then I'm just blind. Many thanks. [[Special:Contributions/206.117.88.5|206.117.88.5]] ([[User talk:206.117.88.5|talk]]) 16:37, 24 April 2014 (UTC)

The whole minor edit thing seems to me expendable. It's not clear to me that anybody uses or cares about this feature. And it's often subjective when to use it. It's never really helped me with monitoring my watchlist either... I still end up checking the edit to make sure it's kosher. [[User:Jason Quinn|Jason Quinn]] ([[User talk:Jason Quinn|talk]]) 22:55, 24 April 2014 (UTC)

:Minor edits were disabled for anonymous users in [http://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/wikitech-l/2003-January/001974.html January 2003] after [http://lists.wikimedia.org/pipermail/wikitech-l/2002-December/001737.html this discussion] (which focused on bot edits and RecentChanges). I found this out by following the links from [//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Minor_edit&oldid=2342236 the first version] of {{noredirect|Wikipedia:Minor edit}} (note that the actual links are broken due to the subsequent re-organization of the mailing list archives). '''[[User:Graham87|Graham]]'''<font color="green">[[User talk:Graham87|87]]</font> 09:50, 25 April 2014 (UTC)
::Thanks for finding that. I've added a footnote to [[Help:Minor edit]]. From that disussion the change was obviously made as the bot flag had yet to exist. I think we're actually long overdue a discussion of whether the feature should be re-enabled. Perhaps I should start an RfC on the topic? — [[User:Scott|'''<span style="color:#000">Scott</span>''']] <span style="color:#900">•</span> [[User talk:Scott|''<span style="color:#000">talk</span>'']] 14:26, 26 April 2014 (UTC)

