:::Actually, there is no trailing whitespace in the rendering either. There is weird selection issue though: if I select text from top to bottom, selection looks like the lines are complimented with whitespace, but reverse selection direction reveals that there is no trailing whitespace. FWIW here is what I get using <code>curl https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fidonet | sed 's/$/$/'</code> (''sed'' command appends "''$''" to the end of every line):
<pre>$
                   __$
                  /  \$
                 /|oo \$
                (_|  /_)$
                 _`@/_ \    _$
                |     | \   \\$
                | (*) |  \   )) $
   ______       |__U__| /  \//$
  / FIDO \       _//|| _\   /$
 (________)     (_/(_|(____/$
(c) John Madil$
$</pre>
