== Moved text, didn't move edit history. ==

I moved some  text from [[User:Gobonobo/sandbox7]] into an existing article ([[Betty Bone Schiess]]), but of course now the article itself doesn't contain the full edit history.  Can this be fixed? --[[User:Slashme|Slashme]] ([[User talk:Slashme|talk]]) 21:08, 4 May 2014 (UTC)
:The edit histories overlap slightly, so it's best to leave them as they are. If there was no overlap they could have been [[WP:HISTMERGE|history merged]], but this is not advisable if there are parallel editing histories, as it results in very confusing diffs. — '''''[[User:Mr. Stradivarius|<span style="color: #194D00; font-family: Palatino, Times, serif">Mr. Stradivarius</span>]]''''' <sup>[[User talk:Mr. Stradivarius|♪ talk ♪]]</sup> 03:36, 5 May 2014 (UTC)
::OK, thanks.  I'll be more careful next time. --[[User:Slashme|Slashme]] ([[User talk:Slashme|talk]]) 06:29, 5 May 2014 (UTC)

