===Reported as a bug?===
Has anyone raised these at Bugzilla, or is the only report that made by the PT Wiki? [[User:Chaosdruid|Chaosdruid]] ([[User talk:Chaosdruid|talk]]) 00:48, 17 May 2014 (UTC)
