::::{{ping|MarnetteD}}: I'm working on merging the page histories, leaving only the original redirect at [[The Strange Case of Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde]]. However, the target page that I have to delete, move, merge, and restore has over 5,000 revisions so I need a [[m:Steward|steward]] to help complete this. Software limitations keep local admins from working directly with pages of this size. I'm seeking one out. [[User:Keegan|Keegan]] ([[User talk:Keegan|talk]]) 02:55, 22 May 2014 (UTC)
