:{{tl|Unblock}} and {{tl|Unblock on hold}} has had their collapsible option removed and made the admin part only visible to admins, but I see that was not such a good move. <span style="font-family:'Trebuchet MS'"> — [[User:Edokter|<span style="color:#008"><i>E</i>dokter</span>]] ([[User talk:Edokter|<span style="color:#080">talk</span>]]) — </span> 14:58, 23 May 2014 (UTC)
