== Pending changes configuration ==

I installed [[mw:Extension:FlaggedRevs]] on my wiki. Edits by IPs will go live immediately, instead of being held until a reviewer approves it. Since this wiki uses the same extension to implement pending changes, what configurations do I need to set to prevent unreviewed edits from going live? I have all the default configurations.  <small><span class="autosigned">— Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[User:Acqirst|Acqirst]] ([[User talk:Acqirst|talk]] • [[Special:Contributions/Acqirst|contribs]]) 04:46, 28 May 2014 (UTC)</span></small><!-- Template:Unsigned --> <!--Autosigned by SineBot-->
:{{replyto|acqirst}} you can look this up on [https://noc.wikimedia.org/conf/CommonSettings.php.txt CommonSettings.php] of WMF. It specifies:
<syntaxhighlight lang="php">
// Per-wiki config for Flagged Revisions
if ( $wmgUseFlaggedRevs ) {
	include( "$wmfConfigDir/flaggedrevs.php" );
}
#Adding Flaggedrevs rights so that they are available for globalgroups/staff rights - JRA 2013-07-22
$wgAvailableRights[] = 'stablesettings';
$wgAvailableRights[] = 'review';
$wgAvailableRights[] = 'unreviewedpages';
$wgAvailableRights[] = 'movestable';
$wgAvailableRights[] = 'validate';
</syntaxhighlight>
:And then look at [https://noc.wikimedia.org/conf/flaggedrevs.php.txt flaggedrevs.php] to find the settings for enwiki. —[[User:TheDJ|Th<span style="color: green">e</span>DJ]] ([[User talk:TheDJ|talk]] • [[Special:Contributions/TheDJ|contribs]]) 08:34, 28 May 2014 (UTC)

Thanks, I found what I needed! Very happy!!! <span style="font-size: smaller;" class="autosigned">— Preceding [[Wikipedia:Signatures|unsigned]] comment added by [[Special:Contributions/208.94.244.34|208.94.244.34]] ([[User talk:208.94.244.34|talk]]) 16:27, 28 May 2014 (UTC)</span><!-- Template:Unsigned IP --> <!--Autosigned by SineBot-->

== Template coding ==

{| class="infobox vcard" style="width:{{{box_width|24em}}}; font-size:88%; text-align:left;"
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:center; background-color:{{#if:{{{deathdate|}}}|silver|#ed8}}; color:#000;" {{!}} Award
|}
I once noticed that we have some template which name I (of cource) don't remember; it is used in templates for formatting the number sign (#), so that such errors don't show up.--'''[[User:Edgars2007|<font color="FF6600">Edgars2007</font>]]''' <sup>([[User talk:Edgars2007|talk]]/[[Special:Contributions/Edgars2007|contribs]])</sup> 15:54, 29 May 2014 (UTC)
:Are you looking for [[Template:Pound]]? -- [[User:John of Reading|John of Reading]] ([[User talk:John of Reading|talk]]) 16:05, 29 May 2014 (UTC)
:<del>You don't need a template; see [[Help:Template#Problems and workarounds]] and use <code>&amp;#35;</code> instead of <code>#</code> alone.</del> --[[User:Redrose64|<span style="color:#a80000; background:#ffeeee; text-decoration:inherit">Red</span>rose64]] ([[User talk:Redrose64|talk]]) 16:06, 29 May 2014 (UTC)
::Strike that - it won't work inside <code>style="..."</code> --[[User:Redrose64|<span style="color:#a80000; background:#ffeeee; text-decoration:inherit">Red</span>rose64]] ([[User talk:Redrose64|talk]]) 16:08, 29 May 2014 (UTC)
:::{{ping|Redrose64}} I don't remember, maybe yes, maybe not :) but to my mind it isn't what I was looking for (code wasn't so simple) --'''[[User:Edgars2007|<font color="FF6600">Edgars2007</font>]]''' <sup>([[User talk:Edgars2007|talk]]/[[Special:Contributions/Edgars2007|contribs]])</sup> 16:13, 29 May 2014 (UTC)

OK, but what could you suggest if there is something like this: <code><nowiki>background-color:{{{color|#ed8}}}</nowiki></code>. And in {{para|color}} user can write both hex color code (#112233) and color name (black). Then the pound template wont help. --'''[[User:Edgars2007|<font color="FF6600">Edgars2007</font>]]''' <sup>([[User talk:Edgars2007|talk]]/[[Special:Contributions/Edgars2007|contribs]])</sup> 08:13, 31 May 2014 (UTC)
:In your example above you can use an empty nowiki tag. Here's the code you need:
<pre style="white-space: pre-wrap;">
{| class="infobox vcard" style="width:{{{box_width|24em}}}; font-size:88%; text-align:left;"
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:center; background-color:{{#if:{{{deathdate|}}}|silver|<nowiki/>#ed8}}; color:#000;" {{!}} Award
|}
</pre>

{| class="infobox vcard" style="width:{{{box_width|24em}}}; font-size:88%; text-align:left;"
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:center; background-color:{{#if:{{{deathdate|}}}|silver|<nowiki/>#ed8}}; color:#000;" {{!}} Award
|}

:Best — '''''[[User:Mr. Stradivarius|<span style="color: #194D00; font-family: Palatino, Times, serif">Mr. Stradivarius</span>]]''''' <sup>[[User talk:Mr. Stradivarius|♪ talk ♪]]</sup> 09:04, 31 May 2014 (UTC)
::Thanks! --'''[[User:Edgars2007|<font color="FF6600">Edgars2007</font>]]''' <sup>([[User talk:Edgars2007|talk]]/[[Special:Contributions/Edgars2007|contribs]])</sup> 12:31, 31 May 2014 (UTC)

