== Navigating mobile interface ==

I'm using Firefox on Android Galaxy S3 to access the mobile website. Is there any way to get to a talk page other than by manually editing the URL? Is there any way at all to do a  wiki search? Please {{tn| ping}} me. --[[User:Thnidu|Thnidu]] ([[User talk:Thnidu|talk]]) 05:20, 2 June 2014 (UTC)
