:Ping {{ping|Maryana (WMF)}} see above <font style="font-family:Georgia, serif;">[[User:Steven (WMF)|Steven Walling (WMF)]]&nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;[[User talk:Steven (WMF)|<span style="color: #8080b0">talk</span>]]</font>  23:02, 2 June 2014 (UTC)
::{{ping|TheDJ}} Thanks! [[User:Thnidu|Thnidu]] ([[User talk:Thnidu|talk]]) 18:05, 7 June 2014 (UTC)
